+// SPDX-License-Identifier: GPL-2.0 OR BSD-3-Clause
+/*
+ * AMD MP2 PCIe communication driver
+ *
+ * Authors: Shyam Sundar S K <Shyam-sundar.S-k@amd.com>
+ *          Elie Morisse <syniurge@gmail.com>
